  "instructions": [
    "In a large saucepan, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the sliced shallots and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the sliced prosciutto and cook until crispy, about 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add the leeks, rosemary, and quinoa to the saucepan, stirring to combine.",
    "Pour in the jasmine tea and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cover the saucepan, simmering for 20-25 minutes, or until the quinoa is tender and the liquid has been absorbed.",
    "Stir in the lemon juice and season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Fluff the pilaf with a fork and garnish with edible flowers, if desired.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
